description: Sensec Holding AB engages in the provision of security solutions. The company is headquartered in Arlandastad, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2017-06-22. The firm operates within 10 segments: Aeronautical, Personal Security, Public Buildings, Legal Institutions, Recycling, Customs, Venues, Nuclear Power Plants, Shipping and Blue Light. The firm also offers training services for security personnel through Sensec Academy and Sakerhetsakademin i Malmo AB.
name: Sensec Holding AB (publ)
